                                                                                             NIST SP 800-53A, REV. 5                      ASSESSING SECURITY AND PRIVACY CONTROLS IN INFORMATION SYSTEMS AND ORGANIZATIONS




                                                                                              SA-11(02)       DEVELOPER TESTING AND EVALUATION | THREAT MODELING AND VULNERABILITY
                                                                                                              ANALYSES
                                                                                                              SA-11(02)(a)[04]   the developer of the system, system component, or system service is required to
                                                                                                                                 perform vulnerability analyses during the subsequent tesng and evaluaon of the
                                                                                                                                 system, component, or service that uses <SA-11(02)_ODP[01] informaon>;

                                                                                                              SA-11(02)(b)[01]   the developer of the system, system component, or system service is required to
                                                                                                                                 perform threat modeling during development of the system, component, or service
                                                                                                                                 that employs <SA-11(02)_ODP[02] tools and methods>;

                                                                                                              SA-11(02)(b)[02]   the developer of the system, system component, or system service is required
                                                                                                                                 to perform threat modeling during the subsequent tesng and evaluaon of
                                                                                                                                 the system, component, or service that employs <SA-11(02)_ODP[02] tools and
